name: To Verify all the section of DEMO page

steps.name: 6). Expand the respective section in the tab
7). Navigate to Radio button Side Tab
8). Complete options on Radio button Side Tab
10). Add details to Web Component Tab
12). Click on the button and verify the functionality
14). To Verify the actions on Links Side Tab
Expected status code 201 and got 201 for GET https://demoqa.com/created
Expected status code 204 and got 204 for GET https://demoqa.com/no-content
Expected status code 301 and got 301 for GET https://demoqa.com/moved
Expected status code 400 and got 400 for GET https://demoqa.com/bad-request
Expected status code 401 and got 401 for GET https://demoqa.com/unauthorized
Expected status code 403 and got 403 for GET https://demoqa.com/forbidden
Expected status code 404 and got 404 for GET https://demoqa.com/invalid-url
15). Navigate to Broken Links and Images Tab
16). Verify fuctionality on Broken Links - Images
